{"segment":4,"line_start":301,"line_end":356,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_long_xiao_yun_father","speaker_name":"龙啸云","listener":"char_jing_wu_ming","text":"久闻荆先生大名，今日得见，快慰平生，只因此行必须避入耳目，是以有失远迎，恕罪恕罪。","tone":"虚伪","chapter":56,"line_start":314,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_long_xiao_yun_father","speaker_name":"龙啸云","listener":"char_jing_wu_ming","text":"堂上已摆了接风之酒，但请荆先生喝两杯，稍涤征尘。","tone":"客套","chapter":56,"line_start":320,"line_end":321},{"speaker":"char_jing_wu_ming","speaker_name":"荆无命","listener":"char_long_xiao_yun_father","text":"李寻欢就在这里？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":56,"line_start":324,"line_end":324},{"speaker":"char_long_xiao_yun_father","speaker_name":"龙啸云","listener":"char_jing_wu_ming","text":"这里本是樊林公的寓所，只因樊老先生日前突然动了游兴，皇上也特别恩准给假三月。在下才有机会借这地方一用。","tone":"得意","chapter":56,"line_start":326,"line_end":331},{"speaker":"char_jing_wu_ming","speaker_name":"荆无命","listener":"char_long_xiao_yun_father","text":"你以为没有人能追踪到这里？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":56,"line_start":338,"line_end":339},{"speaker":"char_long_xiao_yun_father","speaker_name":"龙啸云","listener":"char_jing_wu_ming","text":"若是真的有人能追踪到这里，在下情愿向他叩头为礼，以示敬意。","tone":"自负","chapter":56,"line_start":342,"line_end":344},{"speaker":"char_jing_wu_ming","speaker_name":"荆无命","listener":"char_long_xiao_yun_father","text":"好，你准备叩头吧。","tone":"淡然","chapter":56,"line_start":346,"line_end":346}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_chao_ting","name":"朝廷","type":"势力","location":"京城","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"国家最高权力机构","source_refs":[{"chapter":56,"line_start":327,"line_end":327,"text":"皇上也特别恩准给假三月"}]}],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
